        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1131811835" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7549584908662602774">Overall I really liked this collection of short stories. Fitzgerald is a great writer. My favorite was Benjamin Button, but I liked a few others too a lot. Some of the stories got boring toward the end after I realized that he has an obsession with characters that go or attended universities such as Yale.</span>

          </span>
